snippet.title: Quake3Quest pre-release trailer (credits to Lubos)
snippet.description:
Quake 3 Quest VR. Get it on sidequest https://sidequestvr.com/app/8601/quake3quest
Trailer made by Lubos! Join Team Beef on discord https://discord.gg/S4Ywd39Pyq
Features:

Fully tracked VR weapons
VR weapon selection that is intuitive
Online multiplayer on dedicated VR servers!
90/80/72 Hz support (change framerate "on the fly" in options)
Lots of VR options
Support for BHaptics vest!
Cross-platform wifi play (Quest 2 vs PC vs Android)
Companion app that makes it simple to install mods and mappacks.
Unique Quest Home enviroment included (by Robyer1)
